<simplesect kind="note"><para>If command is nullptr, the call is silently ignored (will be logged in future). </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>This overload is useful when the <ref refid="classhelios_1_1game_1_1GameObject" kindref="compound">GameObject</ref> instance is not directly available, such as in networked scenarios or when processing serialized commands. </para>
