</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>Commands targeting non-existent GameObjects (i.e., find() returns nullptr) are skipped and a warning is logged. </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>All commands are cleared after execution, regardless of success or failure.</para>
</simplesect>
